 WebM, AVI video's online gratis. Verklein bestandsgrootte zonder kwaliteitsverlies. Browsergebaseerd.\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me/nl/tools/video-comprimeren\",\"applicationCategory\":\"MultimediaApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Any\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Hoe lang duurt videocompressie?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"De verwerkingstijd hangt af van de videolengte, resolutie en de prestaties van uw apparaat. Een 1080p-video van 1 minuut duurt doorgaans 30-60 seconden om te comprimeren.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Wat is de maximale videobestandsgrootte?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Aangezien de verwerking in uw browser plaatsvindt, hangt de limiet af van het beschikbare geheugen van uw apparaat. De meeste apparaten kunnen video's tot 500MB-1GB probleemloos verwerken.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Zal compressie mijn video er slecht uit laten zien?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Met standaardinstellingen is het verschil in visuele kwaliteit minimaal. U kunt de kwaliteitsschuifregelaar aanpassen om de perfecte balans te vinden tussen bestandsgrootte en visuele kwaliteit.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/nl\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Gratis videocompressor - Videogrootte verkleinen online | ToolPic\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/nl/tools/video-comprimeren\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 gradient-text tracking-tight\">Video&#x27;s online comprimeren - Gratis en snel</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Comprimeer videobestanden door resolutie en bitrate aan te passen.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 sm:p-8\"><div class=\"drop-zone p-16 text-center cursor-pointer \"><input type=\"file\" accept=\"video/*\" class=\"hidden\"/><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-5\"><div class=\"text-5xl text-[var(--color-purple)]\"><i class=\"fas fa-cloud-arrow-up\"></i></div><div><p class=\"text-lg font-semibold\">Bestanden uploaden</p><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-1\">of sleep bestanden hierheen</p></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-dim)]\">Maximale bestandsgrootte: 500MB</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 text-center\"><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] flex items-center justify-center gap-3\"><i class=\"fas fa-shield-halved text-[var(--color-success)]\"></i>Uw bestanden worden lokaal in uw browser verwerkt. Er wordt niets naar een server geupload.</p></div></div><div class=\"max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-8 gradient-text\">Hoe video&#x27;s comprimeren</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass-card p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white font-bold\">1</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Video uploaden</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]\">Sleep of selecteer een MP4-, WebM-, AVI- of MOV-videobestand.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white font-bold\">2</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Instellingen kiezen</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]\">Pas resolutie, bitrate en kwaliteitsinstellingen aan om de uitvoerbestandsgrootte te regelen.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white font-bold\">3</div><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Gecomprimeerde video downloaden</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]\">Wacht tot de verwerking is voltooid en download vervolgens uw kleinere videobestand.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-8 gradient-text\">Belangrijkste functies</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Aanzienlijke groottevermindering</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Verklein de videobestandsgrootte tot 70% met behoud van kijkbare kwaliteit.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Resolutiebeheer</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Schaal de videoresolutie terug van 4K naar 1080p, 720p of 480p voor kleinere bestanden.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Browsergebaseerde verwerking</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Video&#x27;s worden lokaal gecomprimeerd met FFmpeg WebAssembly. Geen serveruploads vereist.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">Ondersteuning voor meerdere formaten</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Comprimeer MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV en MKV videobestanden.</p></div></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-8 gradient-text\">Veelgestelde vragen</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><details class=\"glass-card p-6 group\"><summary class=\"font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between\">Hoe lang duurt videocompressie?<i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform\"></i></summary><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-3 leading-relaxed\">De verwerkingstijd hangt af van de videolengte, resolutie en de prestaties van uw apparaat. Een 1080p-video van 1 minuut duurt doorgaans 30-60 seconden om te comprimeren.</p></details><details class=\"glass-card p-6 group\"><summary class=\"font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between\">Wat is de maximale videobestandsgrootte?<i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform\"></i></summary><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-3 leading-relaxed\">Aangezien de verwerking in uw browser plaatsvindt, hangt de limiet af van het beschikbare geheugen van uw apparaat. De meeste apparaten kunnen video&#x27;s tot 500MB-1GB probleemloos verwerken.</p></details><details class=\"glass-card p-6 group\"><summary class=\"font-semibold cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between\">Zal compressie mijn video er slecht uit laten zien?<i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform\"></i></summary><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-3 leading-relaxed\">Met standaardinstellingen is het verschil in visuele kwaliteit minimaal. U kunt de kwaliteitsschuifregelaar aanpassen om de perfecte balans te vinden tussen bestandsgrootte en visuele kwaliteit.</p></details></div></section></div><div class=\"max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-8 gradient-text\">Misschien vind je dit ook leuk</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><a class=\"tool-card glass-card p-6 block\" href=\"/nl/tools/video-converter\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><i class=\"fas fa-sync-alt text-lg text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold mb-1\">Videoconverter</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Converteer video&#x27;s tussen MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV formaten.</p></a><a class=\"tool-card glass-card p-6 block\" href=\"/nl/tools/video-naar-gif\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><i class=\"fas fa-film text-lg text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold mb-1\">Video naar GIF</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Converteer videoclips naar geanimeerde GIF met aangepaste instellingen.</p></a><a class=\"tool-card glass-card p-6 block\" href=\"/nl/tools/audio-extraheren\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><i class=\"fas fa-music text-lg text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold mb-1\">Audio extraheren</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Extraheer audiotracks uit videobestanden als MP3, WAV of AAC.</p></a><a class=\"tool-card glass-card p-6 block\" href=\"/nl/tools/afbeelding-comprimeren\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><i class=\"fas fa-compress text-lg text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold mb-1\">Afbeeldingscompressor</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Comprimeer JPEG, PNG, WebP afbeeldingen tot 80% zonder kwaliteitsverlies.</p></a><a class=\"tool-card glass-card p-6 block\" href=\"/nl/tools/afbeelding-converter\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><i class=\"fas fa-exchange-alt text-lg text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold mb-1\">Afbeeldingsconverter</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed line-clamp-2\">Converteer afbeeldingen tussen JPG, PNG, WebP, AVIF, BMP formaten direct.</p></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-[#040405] border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-10 mb-12\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><span class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-white text-base\"></i></span><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">ToolPic</span></div><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-[300px] leading-relaxed\">Gratis online tools voor afbeeldingen en video&#x27;s. 100% in de browser, uw bestanden verlaten nooit uw apparaat.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Tools</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/nl/tools/image-compressor\">Afbeeldingscompressor</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/nl/tools/image-converter\">Afbeeldingsconverter</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/nl/tools/image-crop\">Afbeelding bijsnijden en schalen</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/nl/tools/image-watermark\">Watermerk toevoegen</a></li>